data.name: label4.Text
data.value:
1. Be good: No illegal stuff, respect others, and keep your account safe.
2. Sell honestly: Accurate product info, no prohibited items, and legal compliance.
3. Buy responsibly: Orders accepted at seller's discretion, pay full price, and allow processing.
4. Limited responsibility: SAP Shop liability capped at your purchase price.
5. Bangladesh law applies.
6. This is the whole deal.
7. Rules subject to change.
